name: RFKTR's Fashionista v1.0
description:
Fashion is an ever-evolving and captivating aspect of human life, representing our individuality and creativity. This TI is specifically designed to delve into the world of fashion and generate intricate, avant-garde outfits tailored to your unique sense of style.

It's trained on 512x768 resolution so for best results use that aspect ratio.

P.S. also it helps to generate cool looking robots!

If you like my work and want to support me, you can donate on Ko-fi, It will be greatly appreciated.

You should only give credit if you believe that my efforts warrant recognition.

Otherwise, just enjoy it.
